headline: UBS Sees Sluggish Growth for Conagra Brands, Inc. (CAG) in FY26
summary: Conagra Brands, Inc. (NYSE:CAG) is one of the 7 best future food stocks to buy according to analysts. UBS maintained a ‘Hold’ rating on Conagra Brands, Inc.
